Help Scout uses **HAL+JSON** (`application/hal+json`) for paginated responses. The connector reads `_links.next.href` to determine whether a next page exists.

```json
{
  "_embedded": {
    "conversations": [ ... ]
  },
  "_links": {
    "next": { "href": "https://api.helpscout.net/v2/conversations?page=2" }
  }
}
```

The connector extracts items from `_embedded.<resource_key>` and increments `page` until `_links.next` is absent or the item list is empty.
